description:
Carnival Cravings with Anthony Anderson - Season 1, Episode 5




San Diego on a Stick

Anthony Anderson soaks up some So-Cal fun at the San Diego County Fair, where every carnival treat is straight out of the melting pot, like Thai chicken fry bread and a chile relleno cheeseburger. Before the sun sets, he has a little fun with some pint-sized locals who challenge him to a bubble gum-blowing contest.




Original Air Date: 09-Sep-2015
